Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聞起來好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
